                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/22316",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=lionheart33806",
                        "name": "lionheart33806",
                        "displayName": "Ric C",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Well, I read more about my \"issue\".\n\nFinally, I didn't know that for _Oracle CURRVAL_ worked only in the current session. In fact, CURRVAL is linked to the NEXTVAL previously used.\nSo, it can't happen multiple users problems.\n\nSorry for my intervention, you can close the issue.",
